<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
        .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 10px; }
        .message-box { background: #f8fafc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #cbd5e1; }
        .reply-box { background: #f0fdf4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; }
        .brand { color: #047857; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <span class="brand">e-Swasthya</span>
        </div>
        <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We have reviewed your inquiry and our team has provided a response below:</p>
        
        <div class="message-box">
            <p style="margin:0; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase;">Your Message:</p>
            <p style="margin:5px 0 0 0; color: #475569;">"{{originalMessage}}"</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reply-box">
            <p style="margin:0; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #059669; text-transform: uppercase;">Our Response:</p>
            <p style="margin:5px 0 0 0; color: #064e3b; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{reply}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to reply to this email or visit our platform.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The e-Swasthya Team</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated response from e-Swasthya Digital Healthcare Platform.</p>
            <p>Kathmandu, Nepal | support@eswasthya.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
